metadata.description:
This surrealist artwork depicts the process of overcoming complex thoughts and past traumas to embrace hope. While a woman's head hanging in the room symbolizes the pain and hopelessness of the past, a free-spirited horse figure represents hope. Though they seem like two different worlds, when these figures come together, they create a scene where hope is reignited. This artwork emphasizes that humans can leave their painful memories behind and move towards a hopeful future, and showcases the boundless power of the mind.
